sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client, PVC: Flow 1: Model Prediction Logging (TAS)
        participant Client as External Client
        participant KServeISvc as KServe InferenceService
        participant TASService as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP or 443/TCP HTTPS
        participant PVC as PVC / PostgreSQL DB

        Client->>KServeISvc: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict
        KServeISvc->>TASService: InferenceLogger payload<br/>HTTP/8080 or HTTPS/443
        TASService->>PVC: Store prediction data<br/>filesystem or JDBC/TLS
        Note over TASService: Bias detection &<br/>fairness metrics computed

        participant Prometheus as Prometheus
        Prometheus->>TASService: GET /metrics (HTTP/80)<br/>via ServiceMonitor
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User, OCI: Flow 2: LMEval Job Execution (LMES)
        participant User as User
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
        participant Controller as LMES Controller
        participant EvalPod as Evaluation Pod
        participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant ModelEndpoint as Model Endpoint

        User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Pod<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Note over EvalPod: Init: copy ta-lmes-driver<br/>to shared EmptyDir

        opt Offline mode
            EvalPod->>S3: Download HuggingFace assets<br/>HTTPS/TLS, AWS IAM
        end

        EvalPod->>ModelEndpoint: lm-eval inference requests<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        ModelEndpoint-->>EvalPod: Model responses

        Controller->>EvalPod: kubectl exec (SPDY/TLS)<br/>GET /GetStatus on :18080
        EvalPod-->>Controller: LMEvalJobStatus JSON<br/>(progress bars)

        opt OCI upload
            EvalPod->>OCI: Upload results artifact<br/>HTTPS/TLS, credentials
        end
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over GClient, DetectorISvc: Flow 3: Guardrails Orchestration (GORCH)
        participant GClient as Client
        participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS TLS
        participant Orchestrator as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8032/TCP HTTP
        participant GenISvc as Generation<br/>InferenceService
        participant DetectorISvc as Detector<br/>InferenceServices
        participant BuiltIn as Built-in Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

        GClient->>KRBP: POST (HTTPS/8432)<br/>Bearer Token (SAR check)
        KRBP->>Orchestrator: Forward (HTTP/8032)<br/>loopback
        Orchestrator->>GenISvc: Generation request<br/>HTTPS/TLS (auto-discovered)
        GenISvc-->>Orchestrator: LLM response
        Orchestrator->>DetectorISvc: Safety detection<br/>HTTPS/TLS (auto-discovered)
        DetectorISvc-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: Regex detection<br/>HTTP/8080 (loopback)
        BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: Regex results
        Orchestrator-->>KRBP: Guardrailed response
        KRBP-->>GClient: HTTPS response
    end
